<button class="accordion">What is mental health?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Mental health includes emotional, psychological, and social wellbeing. It affects people's thoughts, feelings, and actions. It also helps determine how people handle stress, relate to others, and make choices. Mental health is essential at every stage of life, from childhood and adolescence through adulthood. </p>
